- S in position 1 (never tried at the start).

Try “STING”: S in 1, T in 2, I in 3, N in 4, G in 5. T and S placements are fresh.  
Letters: S (new pos 1), T (new pos 2), I, N, G. All new except T, which we know exists but need to test fresh positions.  

STING looks solid.
